data/先秦/清华简楚居.txt
data/_private/
**/user_private/**

# Note: raw public-domain sources under data/_raw_no_punct/ (*.txt) ARE tracked.
# Non-public-domain modern editions must stay local-only (listed above).

# Editor / OS
.DS_Store
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp

